{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":132561,"originalJapaneseLine":"「は、はい、そうです。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-yes, that's correct.\""},{"lineNumber":132562,"originalJapaneseLine":"　法王ムーララルー……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Pope Muurararuu...\""},{"lineNumber":132563,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はい、それに間違いはありません」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yes, there is no mistake about that.\""},{"lineNumber":132564,"originalJapaneseLine":"「何故分かる？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"How do you know?\""},{"lineNumber":132565,"originalJapaneseLine":"「法王ですから」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Because I am the Pope.\""},{"lineNumber":132566,"originalJapaneseLine":"「む、なんか説得力ある……ような気もする」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hm, somehow that sounds convincing... or so it seems.\""},{"lineNumber":132567,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔人ケー……なんちゃらね」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The demon Kē... something or other.\""},{"lineNumber":132568,"originalJapaneseLine":"「よし、そいつを探せ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Alright, find that guy!\""},{"lineNumber":132569,"originalJapaneseLine":"　見つかったら俺様が動く！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Once found, I'll take action!\""},{"lineNumber":132570,"originalJapaneseLine":"「既に探してはいますが……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"We're already searching, but...\""},{"lineNumber":132571,"originalJapaneseLine":"　見つかるまで待つという","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Waiting until he's found—\""},{"lineNumber":132572,"originalJapaneseLine":"　悠長な時間はありませんよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"We don't have the luxury of time.\""},{"lineNumber":132573,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ランス総統には魔剣カオスを持って、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Supreme Commander Rance must wield the demon sword Chaos,\""},{"lineNumber":132574,"originalJapaneseLine":"　各地の魔人を倒してもらわないと」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"to defeat the demons across the lands.\""},{"lineNumber":132575,"originalJapaneseLine":"「こ、このままでは……その……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I-if things continue like this... um...\""},

{"lineNumber":132576,"originalJapaneseLine":"　人類は滅ぶ……と、思います……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I think humanity will be destroyed...\""},{"lineNumber":132577,"originalJapaneseLine":"「今この瞬間も各方面では","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Even at this very moment, in many places,\""},{"lineNumber":132578,"originalJapaneseLine":"　多くの者が命を落としていますから」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"many lives are being lost.\""},{"lineNumber":132579,"originalJapaneseLine":"「私達も、各国の戦士達も、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"We, and the warriors of various countries,\""},{"lineNumber":132580,"originalJapaneseLine":"　全力でランスさんをサポートします」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"will do everything we can to support Rance.\""},{"lineNumber":132581,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふんっ、仕方ないな。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmph, it can't be helped.\""},{"lineNumber":132582,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いっちょやってやるか」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Alright, I’ll give it a shot.\""},{"lineNumber":132583,"originalJapaneseLine":"…………","translatedEnglishLine":"........"},{"lineNumber":132584,"originalJapaneseLine":"……","translatedEnglishLine":"..."},{"lineNumber":132585,"originalJapaneseLine":"「長い説明になってすみません、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Sorry for the long explanation,\""},{"lineNumber":132586,"originalJapaneseLine":"　これで今回の報告は終わります」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"this concludes today's report.\""},{"lineNumber":132587,"originalJapaneseLine":"「っだー、疲れた……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Phew, I’m tired...\""},{"lineNumber":132588,"originalJapaneseLine":"「では、早速で申し訳ないのですが、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Well then, sorry for the sudden request,\""},{"lineNumber":132589,"originalJapaneseLine":"　総統には作戦区域を選んで頂きます」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"we'd like the Supreme Commander to choose the operation area.\""},{"lineNumber":132590,"originalJapaneseLine":"「作戦区域……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Operation area...\""},

{"lineNumber":132591,"originalJapaneseLine":"　どこで戦うかってことだな」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"So, where we will fight.\""},{"lineNumber":132592,"originalJapaneseLine":"「っはーーーい！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yessss!\""},{"lineNumber":132593,"originalJapaneseLine":"　それならリーザスに来て！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Then come to Leazas!\""},{"lineNumber":132594,"originalJapaneseLine":"　リア、いっぱい歓迎しちゃうよー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ria will give you a big welcome!\""},{"lineNumber":132595,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ちょっと！　そういう呼び方は反則よ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hey! Calling me that is unfair!\""},{"lineNumber":132596,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そ、それならゼスだって、何かしら歓待を……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"W-well, then Zeth will also offer some kind of hospitality...\""},{"lineNumber":132597,"originalJapaneseLine":"「シャラーーーップ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Shu-u-u-u-t up!\""},{"lineNumber":132598,"originalJapaneseLine":"「今は世界の危機なのだぞ、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"This is a world crisis right now,\""},{"lineNumber":132599,"originalJapaneseLine":"　自国レベルであーだこーだ言うのはナシだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"there's no room for bickering over individual nations.\""},{"lineNumber":132600,"originalJapaneseLine":"「う……珍しくまともなことを……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Uh... finally something sensible...\""},{"lineNumber":132601,"originalJapaneseLine":"「それじゃあ、最初はどこに行くのー？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"So, where are we going first?\""},{"lineNumber":132602,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うむ、そうだな……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, well...\""},{"lineNumber":132603,"originalJapaneseLine":"　一見どうでも良さそうに見えて……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It seems insignificant at first glance...\""},{"lineNumber":132604,"originalJapaneseLine":"　おそらくきっととても重要な場所である……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"but it is probably, and surely, a very important place...\""},{"lineNumber":132605,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ここだーーーーーッ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Here it isーーー!\""},{"lineNumber":132606,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスはビシーッと地図を指差した。","translatedEnglishLine":"Rance sharply pointed at the map."},{"lineNumber":132607,"originalJapaneseLine":"「カラーの森……ですか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The Forest of Karaa... is it?\""},{"lineNumber":132608,"originalJapaneseLine":"（ランス様……）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Lord Rance...)"},{"lineNumber":132609,"originalJapaneseLine":"（娘のリセットちゃんが心配なんですね）","translatedEnglishLine":"(He is worried about his daughter, Reset-chan.)"},{"lineNumber":132610,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランス達はゼスを抜け、","translatedEnglishLine":"Rance and his group left Zeth,"}]}

